headline: Realty Income Corp (NYSE:O) Q4 2025 Earnings: EPS Beats by 170% Despite Muted Market Reaction

headline: Realty Income Corp.: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The San Diego-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $998.9 million, or $1.08 per share, in the period. The average estimate of six analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.08 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
